Spell Shop
At the top and bottom of the screen you will find scrolling windows. They contain the spells that are available in the store and those that are in your pocket. The "store counter" is located in the middle of the screen, and in its lower left corner you will find the prices of the spells to buy or sell. Click on the buttons next to the charm prices to make transactions or cancel them (in this case, all runes will be returned to the store),
